                    Kirin 0.6.0
                    ===========

  Overview
  --------
 * Fragments. Cleaner way of associating native code with Javascript, principally useful for handling Android fragments.
   - this is currently iOS only, and even then this isn't complete yet.
 * Modularizing the build. This is to allow optional components; principally this is affects Javascript
   - build script no longer has a dependedency on Cygwin on Windows - it's all written in node.js Javascript.
   - the build script is much faster now. 

                    Kirin 0.5.0
                    ===========

  Overview
  --------
Initial Release
